    <string name="text_info">
        Quran For My Android" is a simple app that displays Quran text or translation.
        
        \nYou have to enter verse no. to display the texts.
        \n\nYou can enter verse no. in these forms:
        \n\"Sura No.\":\"Start ayah No.\":\"End ayah No.\" (Example: 2:182:185)
        \nOr, simply, \"Sura No.\":\"Ayah No\" (Example: 2:182)
        
        \n\nFor Searching a string in the whole English translation text,
        \nsimply long press on the textfield, and search mode will be enabled.
        \nThen simply enter your target text in the textfield to search.
        
        \n\nYou can do ranged search also. To make a search from sura_no. a to sura_no. b,
        \nwhile in search mode, Enter [a,b] \'Target Text\'
        \nExample: [1,114] Paradise
        
		\n\nWhen a large number of ayahs are distributed in different pages, some pages can
		be skipped simply by pressing long the \'next\' or \'prev\' button.\n
		     
        \n\nQuran texts had been collected from tanzil.net
        \nEnglish translation follows Yusuf Ali\'s translation of Quran.(collected from zekr.org)
        \nBengali translation follows translation of Muhiuddin Khan.(collected from zekr.org)
        \nWord by Word translations and transliterations had been collected from corpus.quran.com
        
        \n\n\n\nIf you find any bug please email to fr.rahat@gmail.com
</string>

